RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT RATE_CODE, RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE WHERE RATE_TYPE = 'S' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' UNION ALL SELECT DISTINCT A.RATE_CODE,A.RATE_DESCR FROM CFTMS_RATE_CODE A, CFTMS_FLOAT_RATE_MASTER B WHERE A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND B.CCY_CODE = ? AND A.BRANCH_CODE = global.current_branch AND A.BRANCH_CODE = B.BRANCH_CODE AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O'

SELECT A.FREQUENCY, A.RATE_CODE, A.UNITS, A.CCY_CODE FROM LFTM_TENOR_CODE_MAINT A, LFTM_RATE_CODE_MAINT B WHERE A.RATE_CODE=? AND A.CCY_CODE=? AND A.RATE_CODE = B.RATE_CODE AND A.CCY_CODE = B.CCY_CODE AND B.AUTH_STAT='A'

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, B.USER_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B, LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST_MASTER C WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN = 'Y' AND C.RATE_FIXING_REQD = 'Y' AND B.MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO <> A.TRANCHE_REF_NO AND A.VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND A.MATURITY_DATE >= (SELECT NVL(MAX(RATE_EFFECTIVE_END_DATE), TO_CHAR(GLOBAL.min_date, 'DD-MON-YYYY')) FROM LBTBS_RATE_FIXING_DETAILS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_RATE_FIXING_DETAILS Y WHERE Y.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO)) AND 0 < (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_EVENT_LOG WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND AUTH_STATUS = 'A') AND B.BRANCH = GLOBAL.current_branch AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM SMVWS_USER_BRANCHES B WHERE B.USER_ID = GLOBAL.user_id AND B.BRANCH_CODE = sypks_utils.get_branch(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO))

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER A, OLTBS_CONTRACT B, LFTBS_CONTRACT_INTEREST_MASTER C WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND C.SHOWN_IN_CONTRACT_MAIN_SCREEN = 'Y' AND C.RATE_FIXING_REQD = 'Y' AND B.AUTH_STATUS = 'U' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO <> A.TRANCHE_REF_NO AND VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND A.MATURITY_DATE > (SELECT NVL(MAX(RATE_EFFECTIVE_END_DATE), TO_CHAR(GLOBAL.MIN_DATE, 'DD-MON-YYYY')) FROM LBTBS_RATE_FIXING_DETAILS WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND 0 < (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_EVENT_LOG WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = A.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND AUTH_STATUS = 'A')
